{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forge your path in The InBetween, an emotional story-driven metroidvania. You play as a Pipit, a young boy whose fate, as well as that of an underground world lies in your actions and choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;...you've met with a terrible fate, haven't you?&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/extras/PipitHealingScene-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737466273\" />The InBetween is a gut-wrenching yet wholesome 2d hand-drawn/pixel art metroidvania where your <strong>F</strong>ate as well as an infected underground world lies in your skills and your conscience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Seek the Vir\u2019s source\u2026</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/extras/clip1.gif?t=1737466273\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world of Aija has been infested with VIR and monsters manifested from it. Elim<i><strong>i</strong></i>nate them all down to their source with your trusty blaster and assortment of special attacks and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Decide your fate....</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/extras/clip_2.gif?t=1737466273\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the world of Aija, filled with i<strong>N</strong>fected people. And it\u2019s up to you to either heal them or eliminate them. Through a combination of fast-paced gunplay and Undertale-inspired turn-based battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Face The Consequences\u2026</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/extras/clip_4.gif?t=1737466273\" />Your actions get judge<strong>D</strong> and you face the consequences in multiple endings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you be the Hero? The Villain?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or somewhere InBetween?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Uncover The Truth....</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/extras/anti_pipit_gif.gif?t=1737466273\" />There are a lot of questions that remain unanswered lying within and beyond the real<strong>M</strong> of Aija.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you be up to the task of uncovering the mystery within and beyond the gam<strong>E</strong>'s story?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737466273","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/page.bg.jpg?t=1737466273","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737466273","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986020/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737466273","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3050000,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Forge your path in The InBetween, an emotional story-driven metroidvania. You play as a Pipit, a young boy whose fate, as well as that of an underground world lies in your actions and choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;...you've met with a terrible fate, haven't you?&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragra